# SEO Requirements

## On-Page SEO
1. Unique title tags per page (50-60 chars)
2. Unique meta descriptions (150-160 chars)
3. Proper heading hierarchy (H1 → H2 → H3)
4. Internal linking (2-3 per page minimum)
5. Image alt text (descriptive, natural keywords)

## Technical SEO
1. Clean URL structure (/services not /services.html)
2. XML sitemap at /sitemap.xml
3. Robots.txt file
4. Canonical URLs on all pages
5. 404 error page

